Philippines’ Aquino Says No Hero Burial for Marcos in His Term

-- B y   J o e l   G u i n t o
-- 
2011-10-12T02:56:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/philippines-aquino-says-no-hero-burial-for-marcos-in-his-term.html
Philippine President  Benigno Aquino 
said there will be no hero’s burial for the late former dictator
 Ferdinand Marcos  under his watch. Marcos’ body had been kept in
a refrigerated crypt for more than two decades in his home
province in Ilocos, north of  Manila .  To contact the reporter on this story:
